# Copy to ".env.local" for local development (never commit .env.local).
# In Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables (same names).

# --- Supabase (see docs/BACKEND_AND_DEPLOYMENT.md §11) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxx.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# --- Web push (optional; for browser notifications after service worker + API are set up) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
# VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY=
